    <name>Key Idea: Using technology is not cheating.</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;a data-sessionid="5453353d-90ec-4c5b-8798-affc98e71156" data-shapeids="4" data-slide=""&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Key%20Idea.png" alt="" width="140" height="136" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_middle"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Some adult learners might have a misconception that using technology to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;solve problems is cheating&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9757@$" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Manatravadi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; Snider, 2017)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;Remind them that tools are here to help.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Divider%20Wave.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
